			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="After the killing of Cora and Roger because Dolor can perform the complete ritual (flag LOW_SerialKiller_State_HighberrysRitualPerformed_00c1e2ab-8752-47f1-b847-51aedc0fb189), a crowd of people will be outside the house. This one of the only AD for that crowd, along the one in the Flaming Fist." />
